OL,4,CCovid: Indian delegates in UK for G7
OL,5,Ctalks self-isolate after Covid cases
OL,6, The entire Indian delegation in the UK
OL,7, for G7 talks must self-isolate after
OL,8, two Covid cases were detected.
OL,10,FIndia's foreign minister Subrahmanyam
OL,11,FJaishankar pulled out of face-to-face
OL,12,Ftalks, saying he was "aware of exposure
OL,13,Fto possible Covid positive cases".
OL,15,FHe met Home Secretary Priti Patel in
OL,16,Fperson on Tuesday but will now join the
OL,17,Frest of the meetings virtually.
OL,19,FIndia is not in the G7 group of nations
OL,20,Fbut delegates from the country were
OL,21,Finvited as guests.

OL,4,CHow India descended into Covid-19 chaos
OL,5, On Monday, a senior official from
OL,6, India's federal government told
OL,7, journalists that there was no shortage
OL,8, of oxygen in Delhi or anywhere else in
OL,9, the country.
OL,11,FAs he spoke, several small hospitals -
OL,12,Fonly a few miles from where he stood in
OL,13,Fthe capital - were sending out
OL,14,Fdesperate messages about them running
OL,15,Fout of oxygen, putting patients' lives
OL,16,Fat risk.

OL,5,Cover killing of Londoner in Lahore
OL,6, Police in Pakistan are searching for
OL,7, two men following the fatal shooting of
OL,8, a British woman in Lahore.
OL,10,FMahira Zulfiqar, 26, was found in a
OL,11,Fpool of blood in her flat on Monday.
OL,13,FPunjab Police, citing an initial
OL,14,Fpost-mortem report, told
OL,15,FEnglish-language newspaper Dawn that Ms
OL,16,FZulfiqar had been shot in the neck and
OL,17,Farm.

OL,5,Cwomen during second peak
OL,6, Women and younger adults were more
OL,7, likely to feel depressed during the
OL,8, second UK coronavirus peak than men and
OL,9, other age groups, Office for National
OL,10, Statistics (ONS) data suggests.
OL,12,FFour in 10 women aged between 16 and 29
OL,13,Fwere affected, compared to 26% of men.

OL,16,Fdepression in early 2021 - more than
OL,17,Fdouble pre-pandemic levels.
OL,19,FBut GPs in England diagnosed fewer
OL,20,Fcases of depression in adults in 2020
OL,21,Fcompared with the year before.

OL,5,Cland reform
OL,6, Nearly 40 UK food businesses have
OL,7, threatened to stop sourcing products
OL,8, from Brazil over proposed land reforms.

OL,11,FBrazil's legislature to reject a bill
OL,12,Fwhich could legalise the private
OL,13,Foccupation of public land.

OL,16,Faccelerate deforestation in the Amazon.

OL,19,Fmonths after Brazil pledged to end
OL,20,Fillegal logging.

OL,7, to vaccinate 70% of US adults by 4 July
OL,8, and roll out the shots for 12- to
OL,9, 15-year-olds as soon as possible.

OL,12,Fmillion adults fully vaccinated by
OL,13,FIndependence Day.

OL,10,A                                       
OL,11,FXTraditional Harley Engines have two   
OL,12,FXcylinders in a transverse V shape with
OL,13,FX45 degrees between them - these are   
OL,14,FXcalled V-Twins. Transverse means the V
OL,15,FXshape is in line with with length of  
OL,16,FXthe bike so one cylinder points       
OL,17,FXforwards and one back. Some misguided 
OL,18,FXEuropean designs have the cylinders   
OL,19,FXpoking out either side - ridiculous!

OL,3,G```````````````````````````````````````
OL,4,FIf there were such a place as Synchroni
OL,5,FCity, I'd be there now. At 8.01pm on   
OL,6,FThursday March 6, 2003, 10 years and   
OL,7,Fa few months after the first edition oF
OL,8,FDigitiser hit the air, my modem died.  
OL,9,G                                       
OL,10,GI went broadband some time back,       
OL,11,Gbut was Forced to keep this old steam- 
OL,12,Gdriven jeremy because I needed it to   
OL,13,Gaccess the Teletext server.            
OL,14,G                                       
OL,15,FWhat was particularly eerie was that   
OL,16,Fit died just as I sat down to write    
OL,17,Fthis: mine, and Digitiser's Teletext   
OL,18,Fobituary. I was so Freaked out that I  
OL,19,Fliterally guffed myself unconscious.

OL,3,G```````````````````````````````````````
OL,4,FThe death of my special Digitiser      
OL,5,Fmodem was the Final suggestion that the
OL,6,FForces of Fate have conspired to stress
OL,7,Fthat an era really is at an end.       
OL,8,F                                       
OL,9,GLast December, I was offered a six-    
OL,10,Gmonth position as first-mate on a      
OL,11,Gmerchant seaman's vessel, ferrying cow 
OL,12,Ghormones around the Philippines.       
OL,13,G                                       
OL,14,FThen, tragically, in January my        
OL,15,Fentire family was killed by a kestrel, 
OL,16,Fwhile walking in the Cotswolds.        
OL,17,FBizarrely, police later found that     
OL,18,Fthe bird of prey was out of its        
OL,19,Fmind on cow hormones...

OL,3,G```````````````````````````````````````
OL,4,FI'd always known that Digitiser        
OL,5,Fhad a sell-by-date embroidered on its  
OL,6,Flarynx. There's only so much you can   
OL,7,Fsay about games before your brain      
OL,8,Fstarts to leak.                        
OL,9,G                                       
OL,10,GJust ask Stuart Campbell - he's spent  
OL,11,Gthe last 12 months thinking he's a type
OL,12,Gof salamander, and now lives underneath
OL,13,Ga rock in a big glass tank.            
OL,14,G                                       
OL,15,FIt hasn't been an easy habit to break. 
OL,16,FI've been well aware of my gilded role.
OL,17,FHow many other occupations include     
OL,18,Fwindbaggery" and "nude giraffe rides"  
OL,19,Fin their job descriptions?

OL,4,FIronically, it was only during those   
OL,5,Fdark, humourless months last year,     
OL,6,Fwhen I became aware of the special     
OL,7,Fplace that Digitiser seemed to hold    
OL,8,Fin the heart of its viewers' bottoms.  
OL,9,G                                       
OL,10,GWhen Mr Hairs and myself began the     
OL,11,Gsection 10 years ago, it was primarily 
OL,12,Gto amuse ourselves and get Free games. 
OL,13,G                                       
OL,14,FBut in the past six months I've        
OL,15,Fbeen privy to, nay, on the receiving   
OL,16,Fend of, a love that is Frankly stupid  
OL,17,Fconsidering it's targeted at some poxy 
OL,18,FTeletext video games section. Hello?

OL,3,G```````````````````````````````````````
OL,4,FIt's safe to say that if it weren't For
OL,5,FDigitiser's viewers, we wouldn't have  
OL,6,Flasted this long.                      
OL,7,G                                       
OL,8,GEven when the Forces of darkness,      
OL,9,Gthe suits, the squares, wanted to      
OL,10,Gcrush it, there was an undoubted       
OL,11,Gvibe, a magic, a sense of community    
OL,12,Gthat kept it going.                    
OL,13,G                                       
OL,14,FWithout getting mawkish, or over-      
OL,15,Fsentimental, it's fair to say that     
OL,16,FDigitiser would've died 10 times over  
OL,17,Fwithout the unwavering support of its  
OL,18,Faudience. You stuck with it, and

OL,7,Fgets scrubbed off school lockers.      
OL,8,G

OL,10,Gbury them. and then you feel really

OL,12,Gsac waving a string of sausages From

OL,14,G                                       
OL,15,FAnd like all of those things, Digi's   
OL,16,Ftime has finally come. It's time to    
OL,17,Fmove on. Grow up. Stand alone and

OL,19,Fa lewd old ride.

OL,7,Gto interact with some splendid types.  
OL,8,G

OL,13,Gtheir part in the Digi story.

OL,8,CHere's a simple toy that's easy to make
OL,9,Cand fun to play with...

OL,11,CYou will need:GA small piece of putty  
OL,12,C              GOne grain of rice       
OL,13,C              GOne tablespoon of water 
OL,14,C                                       
OL,15,CTake the grain of rice and soak it in  
OL,16,Cthe water. Next, place the wet grain   
OL,17,Cinside the putty. Leave for 40 mins.   
OL,18,C

OL,20,Cof rice. You are now left with a piece 
OL,21,Cof rice that has expanded due to the   
OL,22,Cabsorption of water - plus a piece of  
OL,23,Cputty to play with! Have fun!

OL,7,GThe World Health Organisation today    
OL,8,Gunveiled its new penis, which it claims
OL,9,Gis healthier and sturdier than current 
OL,10,Gmodels.                                
OL,11,F                                       
OL,12,FThe penis is moulded in hygenic latex  
OL,13,Fand has settings for both urination and
OL,14,Fintercourse. It is smaller and more    
OL,15,Fstreamlined than a traditional penis   
OL,16,F(measureing a mere 9 inches) and looks 
OL,17,Flikely to become popular with          
OL,18,Ffashion-conscious men.

OL,6,C                                       
OL,7,GVyncent Massingberde, who has haunted  
OL,8,GMetcalfe Abbey and its environs for the
OL,9,Glast 650 years, died yesterday after a 
OL,10,Gprolonged chest infection.             
OL,11,F                                       
OL,12,FA local grocer said "To be honest,     
OL,13,Fwe're all relieved he's gone. I hardly 
OL,14,Fhad any customers because of him - he  
OL,15,Fwas really terrifing. And whenever he  
OL,16,Fmaterialized there was a tremendous    
OL,17,Fstench - like rotten dung. But he will 
OL,18,Fbe missed"                             
OL,19,F

OL,21,Fwidow and two poltergeists.

OL,6,G                                       
OL,7,GJohn Paul Getty, the world's richest   
OL,8,Gman, has hired a team of top           
OL,9,Gmicrosurgeons to 'nip and tuck' the    
OL,10,Gface of his favourite pet ant, Gatsby. 
OL,11,G                                       
OL,12,FThe operation, which was perfromed at  
OL,13,Fthe Beverly Hills General Hospital,    
OL,14,Fconsisted of smoothing out wrinkles and
OL,15,Ftightening the skin around the eys and 
OL,16,Fmandibles to give a more youthful look.
OL,17,G                                       
OL,18,FThe ant, who was 60 this year, is the  
OL,19,Ftycoon's constant companion, and       
OL,20,Fadvises him in a type of ant 'morse    
OL,21,Fcode'.

OL,10,Gof people who follow the religion ofP  
OL,11,GIslam. During the years 2001-09 the P  
OL,12,Gbiggest threat wasFAl-QaedaGwho bombed

OL,14,G11th September, 2001. But from around P

OL,5,CAbout Teefax                           
OL,7, Teefax was created by Peter Kwan to    
OL,8, support the Teletext Festival 2016.    
OL,10,FIt is a server that maintains a        
OL,11,Frepository of teletext pages using SVN.
OL,12,FOnce you are connected to the server   
OL,13,Fyou can use normal svn commands to     
OL,14,Fdownload the latest pages.             
OL,16,FNext edit these pages or make your own 
OL,17,Fdesigns using the wxTED editor.        
OL,19,FThen do an svn commit and your pages   
OL,20,Fwill reach the clients within two      
OL,21,Fminutes.                               
OL,23, See github.com/peterkvt80
